title: Geopandas Error with GPKG
text:
geopandas error when exporting shp file: Cannot interpret ’<geopandas.array.GeometryDtype object as a data type The reason is that there are multiple columns in the geo dataframe, the solution is to delete the other columns and keep only the geometry columns that need to be exported
Thanks to https://blog.csdn.net/spatial_coder/article/details/122071700
